## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ff90a-104">Dieses Attribut kennzeichnet die Methode, die von der Infrastruktur zum Ausführen des WMI-Get-Vorgangs verwendet wird.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff90a-104">This attribute marks the method that the infrastructure uses to perform the WMI get operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ff90a-105">Die-Methode muss die Schlüsselwerte der entsprechenden WMI-Klasse als Parameter annehmen und die zugeordnete Instanz der WMI-Klasse zurückgeben.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff90a-105">The method must take the key values of the corresponding WMI class as parameters and return the associated instance of the WMI class.</span></span>  
  
 > [!IMPORTANT]
 > <span data-ttu-id="ff90a-106">Die Methoden Parameter müssen genau den gleichen Namen und Typ aufweisen wie die Schlüsselparameter der Klasse.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff90a-106">The method parameters must have exactly the same name and type as the key parameters of the class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ff90a-107">Die Schlüsselparameter werden durch das <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementKeyAttribute> -Attribut identifiziert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff90a-107">The key parameters are identified by the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementKeyAttribute> attribute.</span></span>
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ff90a-108">Die-Methode muss allen instrumentierten Eigenschaften der-Klasse Werte zuweisen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff90a-108">The method must assign values to all instrumented properties of the class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ff90a-109">Wenn die Infrastruktur der WMI-Anbieter Erweiterungen diese Bindungs Funktionalität erfordert, sucht Sie zuerst mit diesem Attribut nach einem Konstruktor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff90a-109">When the WMI Provider Extensions infrastructure requires this binding functionality, it first searches for a constructor with this attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ff90a-110">Wenn keines gefunden wird, sucht es nach einer statischen Methode, die den WMI-Klassentyp zurückgibt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff90a-110">If none is found, it then searches for a static method that returns the WMI class type.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ff90a-111">Das Ziel dieses Attributs muss entweder eine Methode oder eine statische Methode sein.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff90a-111">The target of this attribute must be either a method or a static method.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ff90a-112">Im folgenden Beispiel wird gezeigt, wie das ManagementBind-Attribut verwendet wird, um den Konstruktor einer Klasse zu markieren.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ff90a-112">The following example shows how to use the ManagementBind attribute to mark the constructor of a class.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Use the ManagementBind attribute to specify that this constructor  
// is used to attach a class instance to a specific WMI  
// instance. The constructor should set the values of the  
// key properties of the WMI instance.  
[ManagementBind]  
public ClassConstructor(int Id)  
{  
     // Set this class instance to a specific instance  
     // by assigning property values and   
     // giving unique values to the key properties.   
}  
```
